ygData.subject: Re: Giant fire beetle?
ygData.msgSnippet: There are giant beetles in West Karana that look just like fire beetles. However I won t swear to it, but I don t think they were called Giant Fire Beetles.
ygData.messageBody:
There are giant beetles in West Karana that look just like fire beetles.
However I won't swear to it, but I don't think they were called Giant Fire
Beetles.


> -----Original Message-----
> From: Mikaela [SMTP:mikaela@...]

> To: EQCheats@onelist.com
> Subject: Re: [EQCheats] Giant fire beetle?
>
> From: "Mikaela" <mikaela@...>
>
> Unless I am mistaken, since it was quite awhile ago when I was traveling
> to
> Queynos, we came across and killed Giant Fire Beetles in the karanas where
> the hill giants and griffawns, griffenes and griffens play. They carry a
> blue eye instead of the red eye normal fire beetles carry. Perhaps these
> were just giant beetles, I'm not certain since as I said, it was very long
> ago (we were level 18 about) that we encountered and fought them in our
> travels.
>
> Mikaela Tristram of The Rathe
